  },
  "helpText": "<h2>Welcome to Derby!</h2><p>Scan, listen and shout out the song before the final whistle.</p><h3>How to play</h3><ol><li><strong>Pick a card</strong> from your Derby deck.</li><li><strong>Scan the QR code</strong> with your camera.</li><li><strong>Listen</strong> as the track kicks off automatically.</li><li><strong>Guess the song</strong> — title, artist or year.</li><li><strong>Celebrate</strong> like you scored in the derby.</li></ol><p style='text-align: center; margin-top: 24px;'><em>Bring the noise.</em></p>"
